      • recordTrigger

        public void recordTrigger()
        Helper for recording. Has an activated and deactivated state, which the menu item can switch on and off. During it's activated state, it records all movement into the recordbuffer. During it's deactivated state, it saves everything on the recordbuffer and stops recording.
